{
  "texts": [
    "A pilot study of blended intervention was run before the main study.",
    "The aim was to ensure that the recruitment procedure, data collection instruments, and intervention content were feasible and acceptable.",
    "The preparation study was conducted for 4 weeks.",
    "Four older adults were recruited through Purposive Sampling with two females and two males (Mean age = 69.3 years, SD = 3.30) (64).",
    "The participants were asked to finish all the measurements once and to attend a 4-week blended intervention program."
  ]
}